# _redirects – Netlify redirect rules
#
# Rewrites bare "directory" requests to the extensionless HTML files that
# Framer exported.  All other paths (blog/article-slug, work/case-slug, /js/*,
# /images/*) are served directly from disk with no rewrite needed.

/       /index        200
/blog   /blog/index   200
/blog/  /blog/index   200
/work   /work/index   200
/work/  /work/index   200
